cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI. 

The paper deals with video stabilization, which is a computer vision problem, hence cs.CV is the most likely category. The paper also uses deep learning techniques, which suggests cs.MM and cs.AI as likely categories. The paper also involves generating in-between frames, which is related to graphics and rendering, hence cs.GR is also a likely category. Finally, the paper involves unsupervised learning, which suggests cs.LG as a possible category.
